'''''Crimson Empire'' 0''' was an online preview of the ''[[Star Wars: Crimson Empire]]'' comic series, it was made available on [[StarWars.com]] on [[December 18]], [[1997]] and later collected by [[Dark Horse Comics]] in the [[Star Wars: Crimson Empire (trade paperback)|''Star Wars: Crimson Empire'' trade paperback]].

